struct the first 10 rows of Pascal's Triangle. (The trick will be to g
et the coefficients to occur in the correct order.  The Maple command \+
for generating a sequence might be helpful. It is   seq(expression(i),
i=m..n);   where expression(i) is an expression with index i and m..n \+
is a range of numbers." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 3 "   " }}{EXCHG 
